author: @zaafirc369
text: I find it is a good way to learn as well. For example, I wanted to learn about a machine learning concept. Chatgpt allowed me to clear my doubts just by asking some few questions. This is the strategy that i used. I just covered any concept i want to learn into "What","Why" and "How" questions and ask it to chatgpt. On top, you can implement the coding part with chatgpt,asking it for example practical implementations of the code. A great tool to learn new stuff
